Package boundaries

package boundaries
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AdminApp
    Represents the admin application for managing various hospital services.
    App
    The main entry point for the Hospital Management System (HMS).
    ApplicationMenus
    Represents the menus used in the Hospital Management System (HMS).
    DoctorApp
    Represents the Doctor Application, which allows doctors to manage their appointments, patient medical records, availability slots, and other functionalities within the Hospital Management System.
    PatientApp
    The PatientApp class provides a console-based interface for patients to interact with the hospital management system.
    PharmacistApp
    The PharmacistApp class represents the application for a pharmacist in the hospital management system.
